        {
            "title": "Introduction & Quick Reference",
            "content": [
                "NB. On all babies who are jaundiced in the first 24\u202fhours of life phototherapy should be considered promptly.",
                "This wall\u2011chart provides a colour\u2011coded decision aid for starting phototherapy or arranging exchange transfusion based on bilirubin levels, day of life, and infant maturity."
